data.description: Looking to get away from the city, this is the place! Custom ranch home that is just over a year old, sitting on a beautiful 20 acres M/L. House sits back off the road with views from every side, inside the layout is sure to impress with open kitchen and living concept. Kitchen has custom cabinets with walk in pantry, quartz countertops, custom tile back splash and huge quartz island with plenty of room for seating. Master bedroom sits on its own side of the house with an amazing master bath complete with soaker tub, tiled walk-in shower and custom lighting, huge walk-in closet with custom built in shelving. Laundry room with lots of space and separate half bath right off the kitchen and next to the rear door for convenience. The other side of the house has full bathroom and three bedrooms, further down the hall is the oversized Garage which has built in storm shelter and room for all the toys. Outback of the house is your very own screened in porch looking out to the pond and the back of the property. This place is perfect for the hunter or just anyone who loves the outdoors, down the road is Settler Ford Conservation area which has over 7,000 acres at your disposal. Home had recent appraisal and is being priced under appraisal for quick sale as they have already found there next home.
